Based on the statistics in the report , China has organized 22 scientific explorations , 2 scientific explorations in the Arctic by using the " Snow Dragon " ship as a carrier platform in the Arctic , and 2 batches of explorations around the Arctic Huanghe Station by the end of 2005 . There have been more than 3,000 person times of team members nationwide so far who have been in the Antarctic or Arctic to do field explorations . 
" Currently , we are doing investigation work for the feasibility of building the third exploration station in the Antarctic , that is also China 's first inland exploration station in the Antarctic , " 
said Sun Zhihui . 
" Through more than 20 years ' efforts , China 's polar - region exploration cause has played a role in the world 's polar - region explorations . But compared with those major countries of polar - region explorations , there is still a bigger gap ( between China and them ) , and we must catch up with them , " 
