Mom of Ten Years Ago 
It was one day ten years ago when this teacher was taking a nap by using the rest time at noon . Suddenly , the phone rang . 
She picked up the phone , and heard a strange and rude voice : " Your child stole a book , and we caught her . Come and hurry up ! " 
The crying noise of a little girl and denouncing voices from others came out of the handset . 
She understood the thing immediately when she turned her head and looked at her only daughter , who was watching TV . 
There must be a little girl who was caught by the saleswoman for stealing a book . She does not want her family members to know this , so she made up a phone number , and a phone call happens to come here . 
She could of course hang up the phone and give no response , and even scold the other side . 
Because this thing has nothing to do with her . 
But she herself is a teacher ; maybe that girl is one of her pupils . 
She could probably imagine through the phone that that little girl , who made a wrong decision at that moment , must be very panicked , and may be facing the most terrible situation of her life . 
After she hesitated for a moment , she suddenly had an idea in her mind . Yes , I will do it this way . 
Then , she asked for the detailed address of the bookstore , and hurried there . 
As she expected , a little girl with tear stains all over her face was standing in the bookstore . 
And those adults standing around were scolding her ferociously in loud voices . 
She rushed to the poor little girl and held her in her arms , and turned her head to the sales clerks around , and said : " Talk to me if you have something to say . Do not terrify the child . " 
She took the little girl with her and walked out of the bookstore after she paid out several dozen Yuan as a fine , while the sales clerks were whispering reluctantly . Then , she could clearly see the face messed with tears and panic . 
She smiled , and brought the little girl home . She cleaned her up thoroughly and let her go without asking anything . 
She especially urged her before she left , " If you want to read books , you could come here , auntie 's home has a lot of books . " 
The little girl , who was still in a panic , gazed at her deeply before running away , and never showed up again . 
Time passes as quickly as running water , and a period of ten years has passed in a flash without notice . 
She had forgotten the thing a long time ago , and still lives there with a calm and serene life . 
One afternoon , knocking noises came from outside the door . 
A young and strange girl with a pretty face appeared when she opened the door . She had a big smile on her face and was holding a big pile of gifts in her hands . 
" Who are you looking for ? " 
She asked with doubt . 
The girl was moved and talked with a lot of words . 
It was not easy for her to find out from the strange girl 's talking that she was the little girl of that year . Ten years after , she had graduated from a university without any difficulties , and now she had made a special trip to see her . 
The young girl said with a soft voice and tears in her eyes : " Although I still don 't understand why you were willing to pretend to be my mom and save me , during these 10 years , I have always felt that I want to call you mom . " 
The teacher 's eyes also started to become blurred . 
" If I did not help you that day , what was going to happen to you ? " She asked with curiosity . 
The face of the girl suddenly became gloomy . She shook her head slightly and said , " I cannot explain it clearly , I might have done a stupid thing or even killed myself . " 
The teacher felt a sudden jump in her heart , and began to rejoice in her mind . 
The decision she made at that moment in that year could even impact a person in her life . 
Looking at the happy smile on the face of that girl , she also smiled with her . 
